<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ONLY WAITING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thihna hung tung ding I ngak chuh,
 Phat tawmcha mai I nei tau;
 Khawvak I muh tawpna ding chuh,
 Nicheng in I naih deuh deuh.
 Lei thimna hi a beih tieng leh,
 I lunggil hung vak intin;
 Ziechun van aksi haw guol khun,
 Kumsawt in vak zing tai tiu.

[V2]
 2. Buh atten buhvui nunungpen,
 A lakkhawm chanuh ngakin;
 Gimtheih na cheng cheng abei tai,
 Van gamnuom a hungnai tai.
 Buh atten buh lak ding cheng cheng,
 Kin takin lakhawm un tin;
 Khawvel guolnawp pakbang tuoi ding,
 Ken taihsan meng ka nuom hi.

[V3]
 3. Angelten suongmantam kawtkhak,
 A hawn ding phatuh ngakin;
 Kei lungsiet um leh ngawnchang hin,
 Kawtkhak bula ngak zingin.
 A thawm giu leh a Aw giu chuh,
 Tuhin le ka za zing hi;
 Kei ei sapnau leh chielnau chuh,
 Ngak zingin ka um zing hi.

[V4]
 4. Bangmah tika ka muh ngei loh,
 Mun nuomzaw chuh chang ing ting;
 Ziechun hinna thing a pak lun,
 A gam chu a hing zing hi.
 Ka tatna bukim chuh ngakin,
 Hukdampan ei piek ding chuh;
 Gitlohna cheng le bei ta'n a,
 Lungkham leh nat bei ta'n a.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>367</hymn_number>
</song>